festival.introText: Emerge Music Festival Belfast returns to Boucher Playing Fields, Hosting International Dance headline acts and local Belfast talent
festival.location: Boucher Road Playing Fields in Belfast

faqs.question: Where is Emerge?
faqs.answer:
Emerge is located at Boucher Park

Boucher Road, Belfast, Northern Ireland, BT12 6RH

faqs.question: Does Emerge have any age restrictions?
faqs.answer: Yes, Emerge will be a strictly 16+ event / ID required

faqs.question: Does Emerge have onsite camping?
faqs.answer: No, Emerge is a non-camping festival so camping equipment is not needed
